        <ol class="list-decimal pl-5 mt-3 space-y-2"><li>History and goals review</li>
<li>Vitamin selection per needs</li>
<li>Quick, comfortable administration</li>
<li>Plan cadence for maintenance</li></ol>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-14 section-muted">
    <div class="container grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <div class="card p-6 rounded-2xl border bg-white">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold">Ideal candidates</h3>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-5 mt-3 space-y-2"><li>Low energy concerns</li>
<li>Skin wellness support</li>
<li>Complement to nutrition and sleep</li></ul>
      </div>
      <div class="card p-6 rounded-2xl border bg-white">
